<plot>John is a bitter old Mexican born in Houston, Texas. After thirty years of working his fingers to the bone in the moving business, John is exhausted, broke, and should probably retire. John is forced to move furniture with another mover named Chris, who was born without a work ethic and whose laziness is legendary. The result is a disaster. In this 24 minute comedy film, you'll witness a story so outrageous that it can't be told. You'll have to see it to believe it.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?278573</url></doc>
